   "info" : "<table width=\"100%\" summary=\"page for LakeHuron\"><tr><td>LakeHuron</td><td style=\"text-align: right;\">R Documentation</td></tr></table>\\n<h2>Level of Lake Huron 1875&ndash;1972</h2>\\n<h3>Description</h3>\\n<p>Annual measurements of the level, in feet, of Lake Huron 1875&ndash;1972.\\n</p>\\n<h3>Usage</h3>\\n<pre>LakeHuron</pre>\\n<h3>Format</h3>\\n<p>A time series of length 98.\\n</p>\\n<h3>Source</h3>\\n<p>Brockwell, P. J. and Davis, R. A. (1991).\\n<em>Time Series and Forecasting Methods</em>.\\nSecond edition. Springer, New York. Series A, page 555.\\n</p>\\n<p>Brockwell, P. J. and Davis, R. A. (1996).\\n<em>Introduction to Time Series and Forecasting</em>.\\nSpringer, New York.\\nSections 5.1 and 7.6.\\n</p>\\n",
